      "message": "If we feel the need to comment this then I\u0027d suggest something terser like:\n\n // If there are GrOpsTasks that still holding data in these arenas then their\n // refs will keep the arena alive until those tasks are flushed. A new ops tasks\n // will trigger creation of new arenas. Arenas don\u0027t incrementally free memory so\n // this mechanism is how we prevent unbounded growth.",
